  "texts": [
    "Among the ailments that affect the lower respiratory tract, the most common ones are pneumonia, bronchitis, and influenza [2].",
    "Chronic respiratory diseases (CRDs) are incurable conditions that disrupt the delicate balance of the lungs.",
    "They mainly appear as COPD and asthma-causing impairments.Surprisingly, most deaths related to COPD occur in people under 70 years old.",
    "The impact is striking, with COPD claiming about 3 million lives yearly, accounting for 6% of mortality.",
    "Asthma is also widespread, affecting children and adults, with around 262 million individuals affected [3]."
  ],
